It is the combination of key and value pairs  
separated with commas.
It is written in curly braces is called as dictionary.
We also use dict() function can be used to create dictionary.
It is mutable.
Insertion and deletion is possible in dictionary.
It can hold heterogeneous elements.
Indexing and slicing is not possible in dictionary.
In order to accesses elements in dictionary, we keys to access the values of the dictionary.
In dictionary 

In the dict keys can't be duplicate, values can be duplicates.
